    <h1>About</h1>

    <p>All you want to know about the organisation of Hoa!</p>

    <h2 id="Name_and_origin">Name and origin</h2>

    <p>Hoa is pronounced <em>/hoa/</em> and is a retro-recursive acronym for
    <em lang="en">Hoa, Open Accessibility</em>. The project has been created and
    is led by Ivan Enderlin but it is now run by a growing and responsible
    community.</p>

    <h2 id="Non-profit_foundation">Non-profit foundation</h2>

    <p>Hoa Project is a non-profit <a href="@f:language=Fr">foundation</a>
    (french <em lang="fr">loi</em> 1901). It aims to support the Hoa project by
    developing, deploying and promoting the free softwares from Hoa Project, its
    derivatives and associated projects. You can find the
    <a href="@f+:language=Fr&amp;_able=Statutes">the statutes</a> online.</p>

    <h2 id="Support_us">Support us</h2>

    <p>If you want to help Hoa and its projects, you can
    <a href="@f+:language=Fr&amp;_able=Support">contribute in many ways</a>.</p>

